data.description: Spacious home in Emerald Lake Townhome by Royal Oak Homes. This 2 story 3 bedroom 3 bath & 3 full walk-in closets townhome is move in ready. Open floor plan, solid wood cabinets, formica countertops, and stainless steel appliances. Fully screened in patio with a full storage unit attached. Great community & amenities included such as a Community pool, cabanas, playground, and park for the family to enjoy. Only 14 miles away from Disney, Restaurants, and major attractions. Schedule your appointment to come tour this amazing property today!
